===Noun===
'''γένος'''

# “[[kin]]” (abstractly or concretely, literally or figuratively, individually or collectively): - born, [[country]] (-man), [[diversity]], [[generation]], [[kind]] (-red), [[nation]], [[offspring]], stock.

